An easy workaround is to set the column property for the worksheet. I ran into a similar issue when using getColumn with index. After setting worksheet.columns I could access them by key.
Something like this:
```
    worksheet.columns = [
      { header: 'Category', key: 'category'},
      { header: 'Name', key: 'name'},
      { header: 'Key', key: 'key'},
      { header: 'Value', key: 'value'}
    ];
```
